    This endpoint creates a new asset on the server and returns the resulting object.  Nested lists can be created automatically.

If you include a "localPath" parameter, EnterMedia will copy the file at that path into the DAM. 

If you include a "fetchURL" parameter, EnterMedia will download the file at that URL into the DAM. 

You can post to this endpoint with a mutlipart file upload.Create a new asset

